    lesson: 'Execution reviews are full of "must-fund emergencies." The discipline is triage: was the need genuinely unforeseeable and time-critical, or is it a known requirement that slipped and is now wearing urgency to jump the queue? Reprogramming and (for cross-account moves) transfer authority both demand that requirements be real and, for GTA, unforeseen. Framing is not evidence.',
