    prompt: 'You must compress an acronym-heavy budget review packet into a one-page plain-language brief. Which set of elements should it cover?',
    correct: 'Funding status (color, current/expired/canceled, lifecycle stage); legal constraints (purpose/time/amount, CR limits, ADA risk); execution risks (variance and obligation rate); decisions needed (the ask and whether the fund move is legally available); and evidence gaps (what an auditor would demand).',
